{"tid":587840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國跨光譜議員NGO　要求取消311補選　立即恢復DQ議員議席　議員被DQ屬非法","createTime":"2018-03-10T17:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T01:16:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22ec3c5a4487ad75510669febdd03c0fd233533e","tid":587840,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/03/311-hk-watch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F03%2F311-hk-watch%2F&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cac3f642\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/03/311-hk-watch/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/58ecfa82e3df284d3a13dd41/t/5aa101644192022702931c8f/1520501099097/PS.png?format=500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F58ecfa82e3df284d3a13dd41%2Ft%2F5aa101644192022702931c8f%2F1520501099097%2FPS.png%3Fformat%3D500w&h=00b4da49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三一一補選前三日，英倫人權組織Hong Kong WATCH發表報告，要求取消補選，恢復被人DQ議員的議席，事關今次補選經已因為DQ參選人及議員而蒙污! 報告強調參選人受政治篩選，中國政府干預香港選舉，蠶食香港自治。報告要求國際社會緊急關注，尤其是中英聯合聲明簽署國英國。<br />\n<br />\n前英國外相兼香港監察贊助人MALCOLM RIFKIND爵士兼御用大律師在報告序中曰：這份報告顯示中國政府九七年所接受的義務受到侵蝕，令人不安。DQ參選人的做法令人倍加擔心當局早有預謀，要逐步減少香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n報告：<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2018/3/7/political-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fall-posts%2F2018%2F3%2F7%2Fpolitical-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=76ff03bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2018/3/7/political-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections</a><br />\n<br />\ncancelling the by-elections on 11 March 2018, and immediately reinstating all<br />\nillegally disqualified lawmakers"},{"pid":"41b7cc22d9ff1249d61ec450898a3683d29692ad","tid":587840,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"支那都唔會理架啦"},{"pid":"c5191a833465f48db23524e7811263c89f08fe9f","tid":587840,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:35:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b275f9718e213fe24c7a9da0ffecb4482ccc2065","tid":587840,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T21:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3f57d02538faa4ab622f91c9970c5ff005f6df","tid":587840,"uid":25556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"取實佢哋講得啱<br />\n政府成日推啲lesser evil嘅方案出嚟（放生姚松炎）<br />\n成班人就好似㗳晒糖掛住爭補選位<br />\n忘記咗dq平身已違反基本法<br />\n有泛民仲話dq啲人已改過自新添<br />\n政府而家好識撚港豬㗎啦"},{"pid":"635179cad4a8f4d57551b30ec34ebf2a46907b51","tid":587840,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:13:51.000Z","msg":"根本被DQ個班人無資源，未壯大就被人打殘<br />\n<br />\n如果捱到2，3屆先發生同樣的事，結果一定唔會好似而家咁"},{"pid":"0332227e0f8c099f0b187fc31fb7d6573501ab99","tid":587840,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}